flowchart TD
    Input[User input] --> Regex[Regex whitelist validation]
    Regex --> API[API Controller]
    API --> Auth[Role-based auth middleware]
    Auth --> CSRF[CSRF header check]
    CSRF --> DB[Parameterised DB queries]
    API --> Headers[Helmet security headers]
    API --> RateLimit[Rate limiting]
    Headers --> Click[Clickjacking protection]
    Headers --> XSS[CSP / XSS reduction]
    RateLimit --> DOS[DoS brute-force reduction]
    HTTPS[HTTPS + HSTS] --> MITM[MITM reduction]
